Html: Using version 3.3.40824.00, when I add Quickgraph.dll and Quickgraph.Graphviz.dll to the project, whenever I compile I get a conflict telling me that System.Diagnostics.Contracts.Contract is defined in both assemblies. As well, if I remove one of them I still get a conflict with Microsoft.Contracts because we are using it in our code. Am I doing something wrong?
Not really. I've had my own version of the Contract type waiting for the .NET release. I will remove it in the next release.
